{
  "page": "Vaes Khadokh",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Essos.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Vaes Khadokh is located in Essos\"><img alt=\"Vaes Khadokh is located in Essos\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/28/Essos.png/300px-Essos.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"284\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/28/Essos.png/450px-Essos.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/28/Essos.png/600px-Essos.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 47.2%; left: 44.4%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -4px; top: -4px; width: 8px; font-size: 8px; z-index:100;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/8px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Vaes Khadokh\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/16px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: 0.5em; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\">Vaes Khadokh</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\"><a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a> west of the <a href=\"/index.php/Bone_Mountains\" title=\"Bone Mountains\">Bone Mountains</a> and the location of Vaes Khadokh\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><b>Vaes Khadokh</b> is a ruined city in <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a>, east of the <a href=\"/index.php/Forest_of_Qohor\" title=\"Forest of Qohor\">Forest of Qohor</a>, north of the <a href=\"/index.php/Painted_Mountains\" title=\"Painted Mountains\">Painted Mountains</a>, and west of the <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki_sea\" title=\"Dothraki sea\">Dothraki sea</a>. It is connected by <a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_roads\" title=\"Valyrian roads\">Valyrian roads</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Qohor\" title=\"Qohor\">Qohor</a> to the west, <a href=\"/index.php/Saath\" title=\"Saath\">Saath</a> to the north, and <a href=\"/index.php/Vaes_Khewo\" title=\"Vaes Khewo\">Vaes Khewo</a> to the east. There are hills to the north and the south.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiafcentral_essos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiafcentral_essos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> It was originally called <b>Essaria</b>, but it is now known by its <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki_language\" title=\"Dothraki language\">Dothraki language</a> name, Vaes Khadokh, meaning City of Corpses.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vaes_Khadokh&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Essaria was a colony of the <a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_Freehold\" title=\"Valyrian Freehold\">Valyrian Freehold</a>, but it was destroyed by the <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Century_of_Blood\" title=\"Century of Blood\">Century of Blood</a> following the <a href=\"/index.php/Doom_of_Valyria\" title=\"Doom of Valyria\">Doom of Valyria</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafvaes_khadokh_.28essaria.29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafvaes_khadokh_.28essaria.29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Essaria is remembered as the \"Lost Free City\". Like the other <a href=\"/index.php/Free_Cities\" title=\"Free Cities\">Free Cities</a>, it had a contract from the Freehold for limited self-governance in local affairs. In its time it prospered from trade with <a href=\"/index.php/Sarnor\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sarnor\">Sarnor</a> to the east.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vaes_Khadokh&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vaes_Khadokh&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> passes Vaes Khadokh during the journey of Khal <a href=\"/index.php/Drogo\" title=\"Drogo\">Drogo</a>'s <i><a href=\"/index.php/Khalasar\" title=\"Khalasar\">khalasar</a></i> from <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Vaes_Dothrak\" title=\"Vaes Dothrak\">Vaes Dothrak</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiafjourneys.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiafjourneys.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> They skirt the tumbled ruins of a vast dead city (possibly Vaes Khadokh or <a href=\"/index.php/Vaes_Khewo\" title=\"Vaes Khewo\">Vaes Khewo</a>) where <a href=\"/index.php/Ghosts\" title=\"Ghosts\">ghosts</a> are said to moan among blackened <a href=\"/index.php/Marble\" title=\"Marble\">marble</a> columns.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vaes_Khadokh&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiafcentral_essos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiafcentral_essos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>, Central Essos.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiafvaes_khadokh_.28essaria.29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafvaes_khadokh_.28essaria.29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>, Vaes Khadokh (Essaria).</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Beyond the Free Cities: The Grasslands.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiafjourneys.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiafjourneys.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>, Journeys.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_23\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 23\">Chapter 23</a>, Daenerys III.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404090207\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.030 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.032 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 905/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 12420/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4474/2097152 bytes\nT